<div class="cookie-banner" id="cookieBanner" style="display:none;">
  <div class="cookie-banner-inner">
    <div class="cookie-banner-text">
      <strong>Wir verwenden Cookies</strong>
      <span>Diese Website verwendet ausschließlich technisch notwendige Session-Cookies, um den Login-Bereich zu betreiben. Es werden keine Tracking- oder Marketing-Cookies eingesetzt.
      <a href="/datenschutz">Datenschutzerklärung</a></span>
    </div>
    <button class="cookie-btn-accept" id="cookieAccept">Verstanden</button>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .cookie-banner {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    background: #1e293b;
    color: #f1f5f9;
    z-index: 9999;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 -4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
  }
  .cookie-banner-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .cookie-banner-text {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 220px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .cookie-banner-text strong { font-size: 14px; color: #fff; }
  .cookie-banner-text a { color: #fbbf24; text-decoration: underline; }
  .cookie-btn-accept {
    background: #dc2626;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-family: inherit;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .cookie-btn-accept:hover { background: #b91c1c; }
</style>
<script>
(function() {
  var banner = document.getElementById('cookieBanner');
  var btn    = document.getElementById('cookieAccept');
  if (!localStorage.getItem('ifdau_cookie_ok')) {
    banner.style.display = 'block';
  }
  btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
    localStorage.setItem('ifdau_cookie_ok', '1');
    banner.style.display = 'none';
  });
})();
</script>
